{"id":232295007,"title":"#分享 分享我的愛車Kawasaki Z400","content":"居然有重機版了，當然要來分享一下啦！\nhttps://i.imgur.com/Jx81RSe.jpg\n我的愛車：Z400\n目前騎了一個月了，來分享我認為的優缺點。\n優點\n1.坐高親民，小弟我163cm，雙腳踮腳可碰地\n2.有滑離合，升降檔頓挫感都蠻小的\n3.馬力在黃牌級距算是首屈一指的，快速道路輕鬆騎\n4.坐墊蠻厚的，每天通勤單趟1小時，屁股沒有不適過。後座女王乘坐約30分鐘開始有不適感，考慮改厚\n5.很稀有，路上還沒遇過Z400，忍者400倒是很多\n6.車子輕，家裡騎樓的小斜坡還推的上去\n\n缺點\n1.性能街車蠻熱的，常常大腿微濕\n2.懸吊偏軟，但以通勤來說很舒適的\n3.後視鏡視野不好，所以我改端子鏡啦\n4.油耗約20km/L，雙缸車應該都差不多吧\n5.沒有雙簧警示燈\n6.因為蠻稀有的，網路上文章跟影片都超少啊\n7.讓我當初猶豫很久的大缺點，為什麼沒進紅色版本啊\n\n順帶一提，Z900RS是我的夢想，6tan的車好帥\n下台一鞠躬。","excerpt":"居然有重機版了，當然要來分享一下啦！，我的愛車：Z400，目前騎了一個月了，來分享我認為的優缺點。優點，1.坐高親民，小弟我163cm，雙腳踮腳可碰地，2.有滑離合，升降檔頓挫感都蠻小的，3.馬力在黃","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"2cffc289-d332-4d4e-95a7-cae58a1778aa","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-10-14T07:01:04.356Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-14T07:24:00.903Z","commentCount":32,"likeCount":77,"tags":[],"topics":["心得","重機","檔車"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"重機","forumAlias":"heavy_motorcycle","school":"國立中央大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":77}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/Jx81RSe.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"67851794-252d-44a4-ac0c-c551df0fd49b","url":"https://i.imgur.com/Jx81RSel.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/Jx81RSel.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/Jx81RSel.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-14T07:01:04.356Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-14T07:24:00.903Z"},{"id":"67851794-252d-44a4-ac0c-c551df0fd49b","url":"https://i.imgur.com/Jx81RSe.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/Jx81RSe","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/Jx81RSel.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-14T07:01:04.356Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-